  <h1>Delete Your Account</h1>
  <p>To request deletion of your Howdy English account and all associated data, send an email to <a href="mailto:support@howdyenglish.app">support@howdyenglish.app</a> with the subject line <strong>Delete My Account</strong>.</p>
  <p>We will permanently delete your account and all associated data within 30 days of receiving your request.</p>
  <p>Data deleted includes your profile, vocabulary list, progress, and any recordings associated with your account.</p>
